{"tid":847000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雞姦朗想用耶穌脫罪","createTime":"2018-10-04T00:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T04:07:46.000Z","uid":54373,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a0add7ca7323880d848b06eda06a4554b29e9e32","tid":847000,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:03:28.000Z","msg":"C.朗拿度發表聲明否認強姦指控：這與我的信仰相違背<br />\n2018年10月03日23:07<br />\n<br />\n　　香港時間10月3日晚，祖記球星C.朗拿度更新了自己的社交網絡，對於近期針對他涉嫌強姦一事，他做出了回應。<br />\n<br />\n　　C.朗拿度表示：「我堅決否認對我發出的指控。強姦是一種可惡的罪行，這與我的信仰相違背。我非常希望為自己澄清，那些都是新聞利用我的名聲來推銷自己的人造謠的。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「對於此事我有非常清晰的認知，我會平靜地等待接下來的調查與結果」"},{"pid":"0dc6676c1e6f30e7c296910790c67210565d4cc7","tid":847000,"uid":53466,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19fbba1b5a43d842049e56137cd3a4e4871ea68c","tid":847000,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:16:01.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"a5d112abb699a1f25e519fe4917126832e9408e1","tid":847000,"uid":30040,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:20:24.000Z","msg":"牙朗信佛嫁<br />\n<img src=\"http://k.sinaimg.cn/n/sports/transform/20161021/b4PP-fxwztru6741388.jpg/w570e6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fk.sinaimg.cn%2Fn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F20161021%2Fb4PP-fxwztru6741388.jpg%2Fw570e6c.jpg&h=6fec85c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02bb5db53640078a369ff1e33395dd0adaacbc3a","tid":847000,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5d112abb699a1f25e519fe4917126832e9408e1","tid":847000,"uid":30040,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:20:24.000Z","msg":"牙朗信佛嫁<br />\n<img src=\"http://k.sinaimg.cn/n/sports/transform/20161021/b4PP-fxwztru6741388.jpg/w570e6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fk.sinaimg.cn%2Fn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F20161021%2Fb4PP-fxwztru6741388.jpg%2Fw570e6c.jpg&h=6fec85c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"cite